| **Search** (6) | `search_books`, `browse_library`, `get_msc_stats`, `get_msc_tree`, `search_within_book`, `deep_index_book` |
| **Books** (7) | `get_book_details`, `get_book_toc`, `read_pdf_pages`, `update_metadata`, `reindex_book`, `refresh_book_metadata`, `preview_metadata_refresh` |
| **Notes** (13) | `list_notes`, `search_notes`, `get_note_details`, `get_note_content`, `update_note_content`, `update_note_metadata`, `get_note_pdf`, `create_note`, `compile_note`, `compile_notes`, `upload_note_scan`, `convert_pdf_to_note`, `add_note_book_relation` |
