## 10. Code Flows & Data Flows

### 10.1 Search Flow

```mermaid
sequenceDiagram
    participant U as User/LLM
    participant API as api_v1.py
    participant SS as SearchService
    participant AI as Gemini API
    participant DB as SQLite

    U->>API: GET /search?q=topology
    API->>SS: search(query, ...)
    par Parallel Execution
        SS->>AI: expand_query() [if translate=true]
        SS->>AI: get_embedding(query) [if vector=true]
    end
    SS->>DB: FTS5 MATCH query
    SS->>DB: Cosine similarity on embeddings
    SS->>SS: Score fusion (0.6 vec + 0.4 fts)
    SS->>SS: Index match boost (+0.5)
    opt AI Reranking
        SS->>AI: rerank_results(candidates)
    end
    SS-->>API: {results, total_count}
    API-->>U: JSON response
```

### 10.2 Book Ingestion Flow

```mermaid
sequenceDiagram
