### 10.3 PDF-to-LaTeX Conversion Flow (with Cache)

```mermaid
sequenceDiagram
    participant U as User/LLM
    participant NS as NoteService
    participant DB as SQLite
    participant CV as converter.py
    participant AI as Gemini Vision
    participant FS as Filesystem

    U->>NS: get_or_convert_pages(book_id, [42])
    NS->>DB: SELECT from extracted_pages WHERE book_id=? AND page=42
    alt Cache Hit (quality ≥ 0.7)
        DB-->>NS: {latex_path, markdown_path, quality_score}
        NS->>FS: Read cached .tex and .md files
        NS-->>U: {page: 42, source: "cache", quality: 0.85}
    else Cache Miss or Low Quality
        NS->>CV: convert_page(path, 42)
        CV->>CV: Render page to 2x PNG
        CV->>AI: Upload image + extraction prompt
        AI-->>CV: {latex, markdown}
        CV-->>NS: result_data
        NS->>AI: evaluate_latex_quality(latex, raw_text)
        AI-->>NS: {score: 0.82, comments: "..."}
        NS->>FS: Save to converted_notes/{book_id}/page_42.{tex,md}
        NS->>DB: INSERT OR REPLACE INTO extracted_pages
        NS-->>U: {page: 42, source: "ai_conversion", quality: 0.82}
    end
```

### 10.4 Knowledge Harvesting Flow (The Lab)

```mermaid
sequenceDiagram
    participant UI as Web UI (Lab)
    participant API as api_v1.py
    participant NS as NoteService
    participant CV as converter.py
    participant AI as Gemini 2.5 Flash-lite
    participant DB as SQLite

    UI->>API: POST /tools/pdf-to-note (Pages 40-50)
    API->>NS: extract_and_save_knowledge_terms_batch(Pages 40-50)
    NS->>NS: Split into chunks of 5 + buffer
    loop Each 5-Page Chunk
        NS->>DB: Fetch Book Title & Author
        NS->>CV: extract_terms_batch(LaTeX_Chunk, Start, End, Metadata)
        CV->>AI: Holistic analysis with Thinking Step
        AI-->>CV: JSON: Terms with Speaking Names and page_starts
        CV-->>NS: List[{name, type, page_start, latex_snippet, used_terms}]
        loop Each term
            NS->>NS: Fuzzy Deduplication (RapidFuzz >85% similar)
            NS->>DB: INSERT INTO knowledge_terms (status='draft')
            NS->>DB: INSERT INTO knowledge_terms_fts
        end
    end
    NS-->>API: {terms_found: 12}
    API-->>UI: Reload Browser
```

